The '''chordokeylo''' was a [[Music/Legends|musical]] instrument that could be modified by inserting [[Datacard/Legends|datacards]] that each allowed it to play different kinds of music. In [[19 ABY/Legends|19 ABY]] [[Talon Karrde]] brought [[Etti]]an [[tonal card]] to [[Valin Horn]] as a [[Birthday/Legends|birthday]] present.

